    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This deck is pretty straight-forward. Power up the rangers with conditions(tales), sword, shield, use skirmish events to make em beefy and aragorn to heal em.<br>
<br>
Uruk&#39;s whomp em. I like the Saruman&#39;s Reach/Uruk Spy combo to burden the frick out of frodo. (Reach exerts two companions or frodo puts ring on, if frodo puts ring on, use spy to burden him up for each shadow card discarded.)<br>
<br>
